{
  "text": "Here, \u03b5 is a parameter connected with B by means of transcendental equation \u2118(\u03b5) = B. In Bassey and Idiong [CITATION_1] , some exactly solvable potentials were constructed giving rise to solutions of equation (1.1) which could be written in terms of some classical orthogonal polynomials. The Jacobi form of Lam\u00e9 equation is given by",
