      "title": "Lam\u00e9 Equation in the Weierstrass form and Exact Solvability",
      "abstract": "In this paper, we construct some exactly solvable potentials giving rise to solutions of the Lam\\'e equation in the Weierstrass form which can be written in terms of associated Legendre, Hermite, and associated Laguerre polynomials."
